data.description:
Well maintained split entry home on double lot. Newer roof, siding, sofit, fascia, paved driveway. Corner Lot.  Three floors of living space.  First floor features family room, kitchen, half bath, bedroom, sliders to patio. (Would make a great in law suite).  Second floor kitchen which is open to living room . Lots of storage space.    
Sliding door to patio.  Third floor to master BR, and 1.5 bath, 2 additional bedrooms  and closets, full bath with 50 gallon soak tub. Screened in 3 season porch off kitchen, large yard with views.  One car integral garage. First floor could easily be used as an in-law suite.   Oil tanks in basement are currently full but may be reduced with necessary usage with weather changes.
